{"tid":88283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角球場擬建單幢居屋　規劃署拒聆訊聽意見","createTime":"2017-01-20T13:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T06:28:25.000Z","uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e85d906b31c031b957f7f156beafc616855986d","tid":88283,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170117/photo/bkn-20170117173734016-0117_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170117175224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170117173734016-0117_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170117175224&h=dc0be263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北角電照街遊樂場擬建單幢居屋，城市規劃委員會收到400多份反對意見，<span style=\"color: red;\">但規劃署認為，反對意見類似，建議城規會毋須另設聆訊，只在城規會例會聽公眾意見便可，而且每位代表限時發言10分鐘。城規會將於本周五(20日)開會討論上述安排。</span><br />\n<br />\n有份提出反對意見的立法會議員陳淑莊不滿這個安排，認為要有聆訊聽反對意見，她批評「這個政府甚麼態度？完全不尊重市民！不想聽市民意見！市民意見一模一樣便不用聽？」<br />\n<br />\n規劃署向城規會提交文件，歸納反對意見，主要包括北角缺乏公共空間和康樂設施、現時電照街遊樂場多人使用、之前興建海關和廉政公署總部還未補償遊樂場用地、擬建居屋阻礙通風和採光、引致熱島效應、空氣污染、塞車、單幢居屋不合成本效益、單位數目少無助解決樓市問題等。電照街遊樂場地皮佔地0.12公頃，擬建110米高，共34層的居屋，提供240個單位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170117/bkn-20170117173734016-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170117%2Fbkn-20170117173734016-0117_00822_001.html&d=bIkwlEUtBEDcqzqftKfRxGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ccf3ffde\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170117/bkn-20170117173734016-0117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ec9e6c2b16b03f15a6c2b876deb5fd54484562e1","tid":88283,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:00:55.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身北角無乜球場，果個已經係 3 or 4人場<br />\n個位細到仆街，咁都要插幢樓"},{"pid":"cbbb630faba0104fef65c35f6c266705617515fe","tid":88283,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6770ec32670a862dbd40fddc4ec0f0df1b96414a","tid":88283,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"仆街又拆多個籃球場<br />\n以後其他國家足球代表隊黎香港仲有邊度可以練波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760a0abd4fd3ac32874ac559c84091b59353d598","tid":88283,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:07:34.000Z","msg":"呢個球場好撚細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a966423acc8600fc5eee036f790b133c5b0fbe","tid":88283,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T00:45:22.000Z","msg":"根本最適合就係水犬總部前面笪地，我懷疑有人不甘海景受損。。。。"},{"pid":"f205d410c56139117570aeb0344adf144d3395d0","tid":88283,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:02:26.000Z","msg":"迎難而上？捨難取易就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2938addf2ded55891ec5ad9a2d1b903dcf233ae","tid":88283,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本最適合就係水犬總部前面笪地，我懷疑有人不甘海景受損。。。。</blockquote><br />\n個關鍵係臨海, 北角碼頭已經夠on9"}]}